o new 'status' command
	- which database is in use.
	- other funny information, like
		how many keychains are in the database,
		which cipher mode are we in,
		how many entries are in the current chain,
		how many entries are in all of the keychains together,
		how many bytes the xml structure consumes,

o 'version' command:
		add pcre enabled/disabled information.
